00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:01,520
And in fact,

864
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:03,320
they are given by

865
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:07,200
the inner product of the eigenvector x

866
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:10,760
with the state psi.

867
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:13,220
That is psi of x.

868
00:35:13,980 --> 00:35:15,800
This is fully analogous

869
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:18,120
to what we studied in simpler systems.

870
00:35:18,640 --> 00:35:22,060
Wave function is the projection of the state

871
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,640
onto a state of definite x,

872
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:27,820
that's psi of x.

873
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,200
And secondly,

874
00:35:30,340 --> 00:35:33,200
psi star of x times psi of x

875
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,940
is the probability

876
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:43,100
