00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,660
Usual thing,

920
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:27,880
nothing new here.

921
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:32,920
Finally,

922
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:33,720
the inner product,

923
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:34,620
not finally,

